title: Super Bowl Storylines, QB Crystal Ball (Football 01/26)
description:
Will Brinson and Jason La Canfora bring you another edition of the Pick Six podcast, where they discuss the Patriots' Super Bowl experience and how that can and will benefit them in the big game, before playing a game of "Guess where this QB ends up next year."
